<materialsCitation location="Darband Azna" pageId="3" pageNumber="114" specimenCount="30" specimenCount-female="29" specimenCount-male="1" stateProvince="Lorestan">
This species was collected with high density on leaves of 
<taxonomicName box="[1159,1265,1781,1810]" class="Ascidiacea" family="Polycitoridae" genus="Salix" kingdom="Animalia" order="Enterogona" pageId="3" pageNumber="114" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="undetermined">
<emphasis box="[1159,1223,1781,1810]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="114">Salix</emphasis>
sp.
</taxonomicName>
(
<taxonomicName box="[1281,1424,1781,1810]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Salicaceae" kingdom="Plantae" order="Malpighiales" pageId="3" pageNumber="114" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="family">Salicaceae</taxonomicName>
). The activity of this species had led to formation of reddish galls on leaves. 
<specimenCount box="[1160,1303,1818,1848]" pageId="3" pageNumber="114" type="female">29 females</specimenCount>
and 
<specimenCount pageId="3" pageNumber="114" type="male">eight males</specimenCount>
, 
<location LSID="urn:lsid:plazi:treatment:45565D62FFA7B324FDFFF91FFA59F28A:C820BAAFFFA7B324FF39F88CFE6BF239" box="[242,431,1855,1884]" name="Darband Azna" pageId="3" pageNumber="114" stateProvince="Lorestan">Darband Azna</location>
, 
